OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FIn a royal first, King Charles III has
OL,7,Fannounced how much money he paid in
OL,8,Ftax last year - it comes as the
OL,9,Fmonarch said he and the Queen would
OL,10,Fnot be living at Buckingham Palace
OL,11,Ffollowing its #369 million
OL,12,Frefurbishment
OL,14,FThe core funding of the monarchy is to
OL,15,Fjump to #100 million a year, almost
OL,16,Fdoubling in the space of three years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
