FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FUnder a new formula for calculating
OL,7,Fthe Sovereign Grant, which pays for
OL,8,Fthe royal family's official duties and
OL,9,Fthe upkeep of royal palaces, the Royal
OL,10,FHousehold is to receive #99.9 million
OL,11,Fas a core grant in 2027-28.
OL,13,FThis would equate to a jump of #48.1
OL,14,Fmillion compared with the core grant
OL,15,Fof #51.8 million in 2024-25.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FThe change was decided upon by Royal
OL,7,FTrustees ` outgoing Prime Minister Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer, Chancellor Rachel
OL,9,FReeves, and the King's Keeper of the
OL,10,FPrivy Purse and Treasurer James
OL,11,FChalmers.
OL,13,FThe boost will be used to pay for a
OL,14,Fbacklog in maintenance at occupied
OL,15,Froyal palaces, strengthen cyber-
OL,16,Fsecurity at royal residences, and for
OL,17,Fthe installation of energy efficient
OL,18,Fheating systems, with #11 million set
OL,19,Faside to replace boilers nearing the
OL,20,Fend of their life at Windsor Castle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FRepublic, which campaigns for an
OL,7,Felected head of state, criticised the
OL,8,Fannouncement, with chief executive
OL,9,FGraham Smith branding royal finances
OL,10,F"out of control".
OL,12,FKeeper of the Privy Purse Mr Chalmers
OL,13,Finsisted the funding was "not a blank
OL,14,Fcheque" and there were strict value
OL,15,Ffor money requirements.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@PO]uD@ZOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
