OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,F"Expenditure is governed by the same
OL,7,Fstandards and disciplines as any
OL,8,Fpublicly funded body, with strict
OL,9,Fvalue-for-money requirements, detailed
OL,10,Fplanning, multi-year strategies,
OL,11,Findependent audit, and Treasury
OL,12,Foversight," he said.
OL,14,FA temporary decade-long uplift to the
OL,15,FSovereign Grant was put in place from
OL,16,F2017 to pay for the #369 million
OL,17,Foverhaul of Buckingham Palace, with an
OL,18,Fextra reservicing portion grant added
OL,19,Fto the core grant for 10 years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
