OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FThe refurbishments are coming to an
OL,7,Fend in 2027, when the annual overall
OL,8,Fgrant will fall from #137.9 million,
OL,9,Fwhich includes both core funding and
OL,10,Fthe Buckingham Palace renovations
OL,11,Ffunds, in 2026-27, to a core funding
OL,12,Fof #99.9 million in 2027-28.
OL,14,FMr Chalmers said: "This year we are
OL,15,Fannouncing that the Sovereign Grant
OL,16,Fwill be reduced in 2027-28 for the
OL,17,Ffirst time since its inception."
OL,26,@vD@SOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FHe added: "In line with His Majesty's
OL,7,Fclear wishes, it will be reduced to
OL,8,F#100 million, a level that the Royal
OL,9,FTrustees have determined will ensure
OL,10,Fthe work of our Head of State and the
OL,11,Fwider Household can be properly and
OL,12,Fappropriately supported in the
OL,13,Fnation's best interests."
OL,15,FThe new figure will be, however,
OL,16,Falmost double the core grant of #51.8
OL,17,Fmillion in 2024-25, and #27.8 million
OL,18,Fabove the core grant of #72.1 million
OL,19,Fin 2025-26.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
