OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FThe official funding of around #100
OL,7,Fmillion a year is set to continue for
OL,8,Fa period of five years, until the next
OL,9,Freview, because Crown Estate profits,
OL,10,Fwhich benefited previously from a
OL,11,Fmajor boost, are expected to be
OL,12,F"significantly impacted" as Offshore
OL,13,FWind option fees cease, the Royal
OL,14,FHousehold's report on royal finances
OL,15,Frevealed.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
