OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FMore than #28.2 million was invested
OL,7,Fin ongoing property maintenance in
OL,8,F2025-26 to preserve historic buildings
OL,9,Fother than Buckingham Palace ` a rise
OL,10,Fof around #10 million, the Sovereign
OL,11,FGrant accounts showed.
OL,13,FIn 2016-17, before the start of the
OL,14,FPalace renovations, the Sovereign
OL,15,FGrant for official duties and general
OL,16,Fofficial residence upkeep was #42.8
OL,17,Fmillion ` a figure, which according to
OL,18,Fthe Bank of England inflation
OL,19,Fcalculator, would today be worth #60.4
OL,20,Fmillion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FThe Royal Trustees decided in their
OL,7,Freview that the Sovereign Grant will
OL,8,Fbe formed of 20.5% of Crown Estate net
OL,9,Fprofits from 2027-28, rather than
OL,10,Fcurrent rate of 12%, for five years.
OL,12,FMr Chalmers added: "It is important to
OL,13,Femphasise that the Sovereign Grant
OL,14,Fdoes not provide personal income to
OL,15,Fmembers of the Royal Family. It funds
OL,16,Fthe work of the institution ` not
OL,17,Fprivate lives or private wealth."
OL,26,@tD@TOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
