OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FThe Crown Estate's 2025-26 annual
OL,7,Faccounts, published on Thursday,
OL,8,Fshowed a net revenue profit of #487
OL,9,Fmillion.
OL,11,FThe Treasury said the recalculation of
OL,12,Fthe Sovereign Grant Bill would ensure
OL,13,F"a sustainable and proportionate
OL,14,Ffunding framework going forward".
OL,16,FMr Smith, of Republic, said: "Royal
OL,17,Ffinances are out of control, and
OL,18,Fparliament needs to act to slash the
OL,19,Fannual budget to below #10 million."
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@`O]xD@^OU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FHe added: "Despite ongoing concerns
OL,7,Fabout the huge cost of the royals, the
OL,8,Fgrant will remain hugely inflated on
OL,9,Fits initial level of #31 million in
OL,10,F2012. If that had risen by inflation
OL,11,Fthe grant would stand at #45 million,
OL,12,Fnot #100 million."
OL,14,FWhere does the royal family's money
OL,15,Fcome from?
OL,17,FThe monarchy's wealth comes from three
OL,18,Fsources: the Sovereign Grant, the
OL,19,FPrivy Purse and the King's personal
OL,20,Fwealth and income.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FThe Sovereign Grant is money paid from
OL,7,Fthe Treasury - public funds - for
OL,8,Fofficial duties. This covers the cost
OL,9,Fof expenses such as residences, staff
OL,10,Fand travel.
OL,12,FThe Sovereign Grant the monarchy will
OL,13,Freceive in two years' time, in 2027-
OL,14,F28, comes to #99.9 million, compared
OL,15,Fto #132 million in 2025-26.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782514094
OL,3,CRoyal family's core funding to almost
OL,4,Cdouble to #100 million a year by 2028
OL,6,FThe King receives a private income
OL,7,Ffrom the Duchy of Lancaster estate,
OL,8,Fand that came to #25.2 million in the
OL,9,Flast year. The land that makes up that
OL,10,Festate is held in trust for the
OL,11,Freigning British monarch, and the net
OL,12,Fprofits generated are known as the
OL,13,FPrivy Purse.
OL,15,FThe King also has a personal income
OL,16,Ffrom his own investment portfolio and
OL,17,Fprivates estates, which is used to
OL,18,Fcover private expenses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
